data.title: Tributes paid to former housing secretary James Brokenshire
meta_keywords: Read Tributes paid to former housing secretary James Brokenshire and other town planning news & information on PlanningResource
data.text:
The Royal Town Planning Institute (RTPI) and other built environment bodies have paid tributes to the former secretary of state for housing, communities and local government, James Brokenshire, who died on Thursday.

by Ellie Kahn
